{...item, active : 'active'}: {...item, active: ''} ) console.log("updatedData ", updatedData) this.setState({ sideBarData: updatedData }) console.log("href ", href) window.location.href = href } render(){ const sideBarData = [ { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard', iconClass: "fas fa-tachometer-alt fa-fw me-3", title: 'Dashboard' }, { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard/votes', iconClass: "fas fa-lock fa-fw me-3", title: 'Votes' }, { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard/voters', iconClass: "fa-solid fa-users fa-fw me-3", title: 'Voters' }, { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard/position', iconClass: "fas fa-chart-pie fa-fw me-3", title: 'Positions' }, { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard/candidates', iconClass: "far fa-user fa-fw me-3", title: 'Candidates' }, { redirectLink : '/admin-dashboard/ballotPosition', iconClass: "fas fa-globe fa-fw me-3", title: 'Ballot Positions' } ] return( <>
